import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'
import List from '.././components/Cart/List/List'
import TotalPrice from '.././components/Cart/TotalPrice/TotalPrice'
import Address from '../components/Cart/Address/Address'

function Cart() {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Box sx={{
                bgcolor:'red',
                width:'70%',
                height:'10rem'
            }}>
                <Address />
                <List />
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <TotalPrice />
            </Box>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Cart
